  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/c92a0851bb18cb4d48f470f211cfc5af.avif?t=1766240192\" width=600 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the small island country of Liliana, lays Clarke, an artist who just so happens to be a marble. They're having some trouble, you see. They're facing the worst thing that can happen to a creative: artist's block. Following the footsteps of their favorite artists, they're out on the town to find a muse! That's where you come in! It's your job to guide Clarke to their next muse and maybe even help them find love along the way. Will you make Clarke's next piece the best artwork Liliana has ever seen, or will they continue to be plagued with artist's block?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired by the YouTube channel, Jelle's Marble Runs, and the visual novel Hatoful Boyfriend, A Marble's Muse is a romantic comedy visual novel where you can romance marbles!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/a23b64aa763da01a3094547be934059b.avif?t=1766240192\" width=600 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game features a panic attack, instances of accidental misgendering, grief, and the mention of a sibling's passing. Please be advised while playing.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/ac6843fd04feea514d21c5e4aa997da7.avif?t=1766240192\" width=600 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/a1959013b8ee373b53248686f2af3509.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/9c5d0a7fde14b28b3374bb461c969d58.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/c0122b7ba916a043f03185ede880104d.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/4db10d99b25f6c358197e7f7244de948.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/d3f1e405107d039425b986e851cdf573.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/6be275e95f558bee3e03151051e24dd6.avif?t=1766240192\" width=600 height=102 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 romance interests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80k+ words</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ CGs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accessibility Options</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Typeface Selection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Self-Voicing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shakescreen Toggle</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ninja</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mafia</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A gigantic sporting event where marbles participate in numerous sports, such as horse racing and ribbon dancing called the Marble Palooza</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/c92a0851bb18cb4d48f470f211cfc5af.avif?t=1766240192\" width=600 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the small island country of Liliana, lays Clarke, an artist who just so happens to be a marble. They're having some trouble, you see. They're facing the worst thing that can happen to a creative: artist's block. Following the footsteps of their favorite artists, they're out on the town to find a muse! That's where you come in! It's your job to guide Clarke to their next muse and maybe even help them find love along the way. Will you make Clarke's next piece the best artwork Liliana has ever seen, or will they continue to be plagued with artist's block?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired by the YouTube channel, Jelle's Marble Runs, and the visual novel Hatoful Boyfriend, A Marble's Muse is a romantic comedy visual novel where you can romance marbles!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/a23b64aa763da01a3094547be934059b.avif?t=1766240192\" width=600 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game features a panic attack, instances of accidental misgendering, grief, and the mention of a sibling's passing. Please be advised while playing.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/ac6843fd04feea514d21c5e4aa997da7.avif?t=1766240192\" width=600 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/a1959013b8ee373b53248686f2af3509.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/9c5d0a7fde14b28b3374bb461c969d58.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/c0122b7ba916a043f03185ede880104d.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/4db10d99b25f6c358197e7f7244de948.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/d3f1e405107d039425b986e851cdf573.avif?t=1766240192\" width=420 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1427780/extras/6be275e95f558bee3e03151051e24dd6.avif?t=1766240192\" width=600 height=102 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 romance interests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80k+ words</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ CGs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accessibility Options</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Typeface Selection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Self-Voicing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shakescreen Toggle</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ninja</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mafia</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A gigantic sporting event where marbles participate in numerous sports, such as horse racing and ribbon dancing called the Marble Palooza</p></li></ul>",
